Ouch.
I Think there's something wrong with my neck!

16
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:57,120
-I said: GET OUT!
-Hear me out.

17
00:04:57,320 --> 00:05:01,640
You almost killed me, but I'm still alive.
And you're happy you didn't kill me.

18
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:06,160
Why not show me a little of that
happiness by letting me tag along?

19
00:05:07,000 --> 00:05:08,920
Please.

20
00:05:14,880 --> 00:05:17,080
Come sit up front.

21
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:56,720
My name is Daniel.

22
00:05:58,040 --> 00:05:59,840
Isa.

23
00:06:02,120 --> 00:06:03,840
Okay, Daniel.

24
00:06:05,080 --> 00:06:07,680
Where are you from?

25
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:10,400
Hamburg.

26
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:15,160
My ant lives in Hamburg.

27
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,960
