Don't know. You look more like a bum.

33
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:39,840
Going to the south?

34
00:06:40,520 --> 00:06:44,160
-To Turky.
-I see.

35
00:06:44,760 --> 00:06:46,960
Going on vacation?

36
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:49,080
Nope.

37
00:06:50,640 --> 00:06:53,240
I'm looking for a girl.

38
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,600
Your wife?

39
00:06:56,040 --> 00:06:58,000
Nope.

40
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:01,320
Are you in love?

41
