-Energy?

69
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:32,880
-Another word for light is luck.
-Ah, ok, the ring brings luck.

70
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:35,520
-You're really smart.
-I'll be a teacher soon.

71
00:09:35,720 --> 00:09:39,720
A teacher? Really?
That's funny.

72
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:44,320
-What is your name?
-Daniel. Daniel Bannier.

73
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:47,520
Wonderful name.

74
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:52,240
-And what is your name?
-I'm July, like the month.

75
00:09:54,000 --> 00:09:56,200
What about the ring?

76
00:09:58,680 --> 00:10:02,880
It's an old maya-ring. The legend
tells us, that the one who carries the ring, -

77
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:05,920
can recognize luck.

78
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:10,800
You will soon meet a woman that
also carry a symbol of the sun.

79
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:15,720
It's only she that can bring you 
true happiness.

80
00:10:16,520 --> 00:10:19,160
-How much?
-50.

81
00:10:19,360 --> 00:10:22,200
-Don't you like it?
-Yes, but...

82
00:10:22,400 --> 00:10:25,440
Why don't you fight a little for it then?

83
00:10:27,880 --> 00:10:29,480
-Ok, 30.
-40.

84
00:10:29,680 --> 00:10:32,960
