But I really want the ring.

85
00:10:33,160 --> 00:10:37,800
Ok, but only because I like you.

86
00:10:40,080 --> 00:10:41,840
-Thank you.
-Wait.

87
00:10:42,520 --> 00:10:45,840
This is tonight. Stop by.

88
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,760
Thank you so much.

89
00:10:50,160 --> 00:10:52,520
-I'm looking forward to it.
-Me to.

90
00:10:52,720 --> 00:10:54,640
Bye.

91
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,800
-July?
-Yes?

92
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:10,560
-What was that?
-That was Daniel Bannier.

93
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:15,240
Yes, I got that, but what's
so special about him?

94
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:22,000
He's got something deep inside of
him, waiting to be released.

95
00:11:22,760 --> 00:11:24,000
Like what?

96
00:11:27,520 --> 00:11:31,600
-Hey! 1.person, singular, teacher!
-Hello, Kodjo.

97
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:40,120
I'm going to Jamaica, to drink
cold pina colada, smoke weed, -

98
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:45,440
- and look for the Kini sisters.
Do you know the Kini sisters?

99
00:11:45,880 --> 00:11:50,400
-Don't think so, Kodjo.
-Bikini and zukini.

100
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:54,880
-Where are you going on vacation?
