227
00:25:15,520 --> 00:25:17,160
Unbeliveable.

228
00:25:19,280 --> 00:25:20,960
One moment.

229
00:25:43,800 --> 00:25:46,200
We could stay here.

230
00:25:46,880 --> 00:25:48,720
In Bayern?

231
00:25:50,440 --> 00:25:53,040
The sky is blue everywhere.

232
00:25:56,720 --> 00:26:01,080
Hei! It's a new day tomorrow, or what?

233
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:05,160
I'm sorry, but we don't have
two single rooms left.

234
00:26:05,360 --> 00:26:10,200
