comfortable sleeping positions.

241
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,640
Is that so?

242
00:27:16,600 --> 00:27:19,400
OK, who will spoon whom?

243
00:27:20,440 --> 00:27:22,480
You'll spoon me.

244
00:27:40,840 --> 00:27:43,680
Mmmm, it is really comfortable.

245
00:27:44,400 --> 00:27:46,880
Really nice.

246
00:28:13,840 --> 00:28:15,360
Fuck.

247
00:28:18,480 --> 00:28:22,040
We'll head south, through Italia
to Bari, and take the ferry boat to -

248
00:28:22,280 --> 00:28:26,680
Greece, and then to Turky.

